                "html": "<table><tr><td>Parameters</td><td>Value</td></tr><tr><td>Total Chip size</td><td>6.9 mm×6.9 mm</td></tr><tr><td>Proof mass</td><td>1.27 mg</td></tr><tr><td>Lever amplification ratio</td><td>23</td></tr><tr><td>CESP</td><td>0.4 pF</td></tr><tr><td>gESP</td><td>4 um</td></tr><tr><td>The resonant frequency</td><td>201.83 kHz</td></tr><tr><td>Scale factor</td><td>440 Hz/g</td></tr></table>",
                "table_type": "simple_table",
