        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "The Simulink model of the open loop sensor system is shown in the Figure 2.  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "H_{ml}(s)"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " is a transfer function of the proof mass, which is modeled a second-order mass-damper-spring system.  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "F(s)"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " is an electrostatic force generated by the sensitivity enhancing structure, and the nonlinear effect of  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "F(s)"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " is concerned to soften the spring stiffness.  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "K_{1}"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " is the force amplification ratio of the micro-levers.  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "H_{m2}(s)"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " is a transfer function of the resonator, which is also modeled a second-order mass-damper-spring system.  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "K_{2}"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " is the amplification ratio of the transimpedance amplifier and  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "f_{n}"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " is a frequency "
                    }
                ]
            },
