                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " applied to the back-to-back parallel plate capacitors, the sensitivity of accelerometer is increased (see Figure 3 inset). For  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "V_{BP} = 60\\mathrm{V}"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " applied on the actuator, the sensitivity can be boosted up 3 times higher than original value where the nonlinearity of the accelerometer is slight increased to  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
