        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "This paper presents a novel method to enhance sensitivity of MEMS resonant accelerometer by using electrostatic spring softening effect. Both simulation and experimental study demonstrated that this method can enhance sensitivity of sensor. In future work, the other metrics of this sensor will be investigated. The close-loop interface circuit of the sensor will be designed and optimized in order to implement a kind of high performance accelerometers. "
                    }
                ]
            },
